<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="Affiliate disclosure for Cat Gear Index.">
  <article class="article-shell">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="lead">Some links on Cat Gear Index may become affiliate links. If you click a link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you.</p>
    <p>Affiliate relationships must not determine whether a product is included, excluded, or described as suitable for a specific use case. Product pages should clearly separate facts, limitations, and editorial judgment.</p>
    <p>Before adding affiliate links, confirm the terms of each program and keep disclosures visible near monetized recommendations.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
